{"_id":"8GYZ5OtI5Qz12vA5","name":"Crit Table I: All 0-Level Characters and All Wizards","permission":{"default":0,"wWErSsSXezizF0nw":3},"folder":"","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.gwfpcBe06bnqlh43"}},"content":"<p>pg. 82</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>@Compendium[dcc-core-book.dcc-core-crits-and-fumbles.1NIawYOcDNXjgJDO]{Crit Table I: All 0-Level Characters and All Wizards}</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\"><colgroup width=\"70\"></colgroup> <colgroup width=\"1031\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\"><strong>Roll</strong></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><strong>Result</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">0 or less</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Force of blow shivers your weapon free of your grasp. Inflict +[[/roll 1d6]] damage with this strike and you are disarmed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Opportunistic strike. Inflict +[[/roll 1d3]] damage with this strike.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Foe jabbed in the eye! Ugly bruising and inflict +[[/roll 1d4]] damage with this strike.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Stunning crack to forehead. Inflict +[[/roll 1d3]] damage with this strike, and the foe falls to the bottom of the initiative count next round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Strike to foe&rsquo;s kneecap. Inflict +[[/roll 1d4]] damage with this strike and the foe suffers a -10&rsquo; penalty to speed until healed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Solid strike to torso. Inflict +[[/roll 1d6]] damage with this strike.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Lucky strike disarms foe. You gain a free attack if the enemy stoops to retrieve his weapon.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Smash foe&rsquo;s hand. Inflict +[[/roll 2d3]] damage with this strike. You break two of the enemy&rsquo;s fingers.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Numbing strike! Cursing in agony, the foe is unable to attack next round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">9</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Smash foe&rsquo;s nose. Inflict +[[/roll 2d4]] damage with this strike and blood streams down the enemy&rsquo;s face.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">10</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Foe trips on his own feet and falls prone for the remainder of the round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">11</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Piercing strike. Inflict +[[/roll 2d4]] damage with this strike.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">12</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Strike to groin. The foe must make a DC 15 Fort save or spend the next two rounds retching.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">13</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Blow smashes foe&rsquo;s ankle; his movement speed is reduced by half.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">14</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Strike grazes temple; blood blinds the foe for [[/roll 1d3]] rounds.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">15</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Stab enemy&rsquo;s weapon hand. The weapon is lost and knocked [[/roll 1d10+5]] feet away.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">16</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Narrowly avoid foe&rsquo;s counterstrike! Inflict normal damage and make another attack roll. If the second attack hits, you inflict an additional +[[/roll 1d6]] damage.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">17</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Blow to throat. Foe staggers around for 2 rounds and is unable to speak, cast spells, or attack.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">18</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Foe falls into your attack. He takes +[[/roll 2d6]] damage from the strike and curses your luck.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">19</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Miracle strike. The foe must make a DC 20 Fort save or fall unconscious.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" height=\"17\">20</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Lucky blow dents foe&rsquo;s skull! Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike. If the foe has no helm, he suffers a permanent loss of [[/roll 1d4]] Int.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em><span class=\"fontstyle0\">These footnotes apply to crit tables where indicated:</span></em></p>\n<p><em><span class=\"fontstyle2\">* Magical weapons never break due to critical fumbles. The target is disarmed instead, the weapon landing [[/roll 1d10+5]] feet away.</span></em></p>\n<p><em><span class=\"fontstyle2\">** A PC overcome by battle rage may temporarily expend points of his Personality or Intelligence score to enhance the damage on his critical hit. For every ability point he expends, he adds +[[/roll 1d12]] to his damage roll. </span></em></p>\n<p><em><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Ability scores lost in this way return as the warrior heals. Each day thereafter where he does not succumb to battle rage, he recovers 1 point of the affected ability score. This rate is doubled if the character rests.</span></em></p>"}
